[Student "S"]
{The bidding has been as shown.   

If you bid 1\S now it would be showing a 5-card \S suit. So instead you make a Negative Double. Partner jumps to 2\S.  

Partner's jump shows a Medium hand, 16 - 18 points. Add your 11 and you have enough for game so you bid it.}

